\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qc\b\f0\fs32\lang9 JAVA CODE CONVENTIONS\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\fs28 INTRODUCTION:\fs32\par
\b0\fs24 Code conventions are important to programmers for a number of reasons:\par

\pard{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf2\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1  Code conventions improve the readability of the software, allowing engineers to understand new code more quickly and thoroughly.\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}\f1  Hardly any software is maintained for its whole life by the original author.\f0\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs28\lang1033 JAVA SOURCE FILE EXAMPLE:-\lang9\par
